data.description: Welcome to this expansive and beautifully appointed Northwood home! This residence exudes sophistication and classic charm. Generously sized living spaces effortlessly cater to everyday life and entertaining. The main house features 3 beds and 2 baths, complemented by two 1 bed/1 bath studios. The open floor plan allows flexibility in room utilization. Large windows bathe the interiors in natural light, enhancing the inviting atmosphere. Noteworthy features include a home generator, new metal roof, well, irrigation pump, hurricane impact windows, and a saltwater heated pool. Two Airbnb units, totaling 5 bedrooms, offer investors a chance to diversify portfolios. Whether for Airbnb income or personal use, this remarkable property near the beach, PBI, and downtown WPB awaits your enjoyment!
